oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kinsall reclining in a chair
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall reclining in a chair. He is smoking from a tobacco pipe and has a drink in his hand. Photograph was taken at his home while he was stationed in Nagoya, Japan.
